<ab>Den erbern weysen, dem richter und den gesworen scheppfen des geriht der
                        stat czu <expan>Meidb<ex>ur</ex>g,</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> besundern guten freunden</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Erbern, weysen, besunder <expan>lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunden</ex></expan>, uns hat <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan>
                        Görg Stromeir, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er,</ex></expan> wie er von <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        und <expan>seine<ex>r</ex></expan> gesellschaft wegen, auch
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan>, etwaz sache czu handeln hab mit
                                <expan>Henne<ex>n</ex></expan> Weiszkopf und Jacob Raten,
                                <expan>vormund<ex>en</ex></expan> des Hansen
                                <expan>Maurici<ex>us</ex></expan>
<expan>elich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>witib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>selige<ex>n</ex></expan> bey ew von schulde wegen, als in dieselb
                        witib schuldig <expan>blib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sey und
                            <expan>gelte<ex>n</ex></expan> sülle, als das
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> Hans Gruber, des
                            <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan> und <expan>seine<ex>r</ex></expan>
                        gesellschaft <expan>dien<ex>er,</ex></expan> selber auch wol
                                <expan>fürg<ex>eben</ex></expan> wirdt.
                            <expan>Ro<ex>gamus,</ex></expan> daz ir
                            <expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Hanse<ex>n</ex></expan> Gruber <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>fürderl<ex>ich</ex></expan> und <expan>beholffe<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        sein wöllet, daz im <expan>dies<ex>elben</ex></expan> schulde von des
                                <expan>obg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan> und <expan>sein<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ges<ex>ellschaft</ex></expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> geriht und beczalt werd
                            <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>unv<ex>er</ex>czog<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>sleu<ex>nig</ex></expan> reht widerfar. Als etc. Das
                                <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
